OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThis evening
OL,6,Fwill be dry with some sunshine. Then
OL,7,Fthe rest of the night will remain dry
OL,8,Fwith prolonged clear periods. Fresh
OL,9,Fsoutherly winds, easing later.
OL,10,
OL,11,CFriday:FMost of the day will be dry
OL,12,Fwith some hazy sunshine. High cloud
OL,13,Fthickening through the afternoon to
OL,14,Fbring the odd light shower.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FCloudy
OL,17,Fover the weekend with the chance of a
OL,18,Ffew showers, but some dry weather too.
OL,19,FEarly rain on Monday followed by
OL,20,Fshowers, turning colder.
